<HL>
   U.S. Wins Limit on IMF Resource Boost,
   But Next Review Date Is Pushed Ahead
   ----
   By Peter Truell
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/09/90
</DATE>
